{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"382613a3c2","title":"给欧阳山尊、朱丹、成随的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8641e4adab","index":0,"year":1942,"month":11,"day":23,"articleId":"382613a3c2"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji17","name":"毛泽东全集第17卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji17.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji17":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"aeec77957e","type":"paragraph","text":"给欧阳山尊、朱丹、成随的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"382613a3c2"},{"id":"e31b5d10a3","type":"paragraph","text":"（1942年11月23日）欧阳山尊、朱丹、成萌同志你们的信收到了，感谢你们！你们的剧我以为是好的，延安及边区正需看反映敌后斗争生活的戏剧，希望多演一些这类的戏敬礼！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"382613a3c2"},{"id":"deb1f46b5d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"382613a3c2"},{"id":"f8a2b2d037","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月二十三日[1]欧阳山算（1914-2009），湖南润阳人。曾任八路军-二O师致治部我手剧社社长。1942年10月至1943年4月任鲁迅艺术文学院晋西北分院院长。来丹（1913-1978），后改名未丹西，北京人。当时任八路军一二O与政治部战斗剧社副社长。成前（1917-1984），上海松江人。当时任八路军-二O师政治部战斗剧社政治指导员。2]指成葡等创作的反映当时数后寻争生活的《察算的乡村》《荒村之夜》《虎列拉》《自家人认自家人》《求丽》等剧。1942年冬，八路穿一二O","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"382613a3c2"}],"page":{"id":"61460fda77","publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"382613a3c2","start":285,"end":285}}}},"__N_SSG":true}